site_title: Among Us Character Bookmark by Wilson Lee

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Among Us there is an Imposter!!! I was inspired to make this Among Us Character bookmark and within a few hours, here it is. This is the Among Us Character Bookmark by Me, Wilson Lee. No scissors, no glue, pure origami bookmark. Try it out, I hope you like it. Learn it in less than a minute! Enjoy!!! If this tutorial is too fast, check the follow along version here : https://youtu.be/c4hs_9jXnpk Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
